    have h2 : q ≠ ∞ := by simp
    have h3 : r ≠ ∞ := by simp
```

Now we need to prove the inequality when `p = ∞`. The Holder triple condition `ENNReal.HolderTriple ∞ q r` implies `1/∞ + 1/q = 1/r`, which means `1/q = 1/r`, so `q = r`.

```tactics
